loads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.30.02-585x580.jpg 585w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.30.02-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.30.02.jpg 676w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 585px" /></a>▲馬鞍山富安花園出沙田九龍及往大埔吐露港公路方向，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident">香港突發事故報料區</a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290552545_10160113833418988_5203202819452267958_n-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107910" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290552545_10160113833418988_5203202819452267958_n-2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290552545_10160113833418988_5203202819452267958_n-2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290552545_10160113833418988_5203202819452267958_n-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290552545_10160113833418988_5203202819452267958_n-2.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲太子道東入觀塘，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident">香港突發事故報料區</a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290745138_10159092369002965_2218722262877597786_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107911" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290745138_10159092369002965_2218722262877597786_n-440x580.jpg" alt="" width="440" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290745138_10159092369002965_2218722262877597786_n-440x580.jpg 440w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290745138_10159092369002965_2218722262877597786_n.jpg 526w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 440px" /></a>▲吐露港公路，圖片來源：香港突發事故報料區</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288649312_364345935724124_5856056720257947716_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107914" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288649312_364345935724124_5856056720257947716_n-694x548.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="548" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288649312_364345935724124_5856056720257947716_n-694x548.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288649312_364345935724124_5856056720257947716_n.jpg 696w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲觀塘轉上前往將軍澳，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident">香港突發事故報料區</a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288840096_355262333354656_604342692887407511_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288840096_355262333354656_604342692887407511_n-585x580.jpg" alt="" width="585" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288840096_355262333354656_604342692887407511_n-585x580.jpg 585w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288840096_355262333354656_604342692887407511_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288840096_355262333354656_604342692887407511_n.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 585px" /></a>▲吐露港公路近廣福，圖片來源：香港突發事故報料區 <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288772564_860619851582884_828248980535635464_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288772564_860619851582884_828248980535635464_n-653x580.jpg" alt="" width="653" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288772564_860619851582884_828248980535635464_n-653x580.jpg 653w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/288772564_860619851582884_828248980535635464_n.jpg 698w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 653px" /></a>▲西九龍，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident">香港突發事故報料區</a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289390490_725409592061526_1982370302648755565_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289390490_725409592061526_1982370302648755565_n-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289390490_725409592061526_1982370302648755565_n-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289390490_725409592061526_1982370302648755565_n.jpg 731w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident">香港突發事故報料區</a></p><p>在 Facebook 不少群組有不少市民發出帖文，指下班時出現人潮，路面亦出現嚴重車龍。市民報告的地區包括有吐露港公路、旺角彌敦道、太子道西入觀塘、觀塘主要路段都出現嚴重車龍，而大老山隧道、觀塘前往將軍澳、西九龍、鰂魚涌則出現不明的封路措施。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107912" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/289410904_5270247313068469_8861982350843231153_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107913" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290370181_1345421085989057_6638963002491081618_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲觀塘地鐵站出現人龍</p><p>而根據 Google 地圖顯示的交通資訊，全港多個地方出現擠塞，包括東隧、東九龍主要通道如觀塘道、機場隧道至加士居道天橋、將軍澳隧道公路等都出現車多擠塞情況。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.51-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.51-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.51-768x495.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.51.jpg 801w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲左起機場隧道至加士居道天橋、太子道東、觀塘道交通插塞，圖片來源：Google Maps 截圖<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-19.37.58.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium w