ploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-302-at-6_09_46-PM.png" alt="" width="411" height="172" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-30-at-6.11.01-PM.png" alt="" width="222" height="82" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/djihk/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">香港無人機航拍會</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">但事實上，警方在今天已經發出正式的公告，指出會在 6 月 30 日正午 12 時至晚上 11 時 59 分，以及 7 月 1 日上午 6 時正至下午 4 時正期間，將香港劃為限制飛行區。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1107885 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-416x900.jpg" alt="" width="416" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-768x1662.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/290359152_755005662297015_7771308179767030034_n-scaled.jpg 1183w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 416px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：香港無人機航拍會、<a href="https://esua.cad.gov.hk/web/?lang=zh_TW">香港民航處</a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
