</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>海關揭香港 Tesla Model 3/Y    將有 Enhanced Autopilot 可選配項目</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/30/enhanced-autopilot/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=enhanced-autopilot</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 30 Jun 2022 10:37:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[Auto Pilot]]></category><category><![CDATA[Model 3]]></category><category><![CDATA[Model Y]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tesla]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1107859</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>根據香港海關網頁最新資訊，Tesla Model 3、Model Y 的可選配項目中，會加入「ENHANCED [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>根據香港海關網頁最新資訊，Tesla Model 3、Model Y 的可選配項目中，會加入「ENHANCED AUTOPILOT」選項，相信官方會在稍後有正式公佈。</p><p>根據香港海關的汽車首次登記稅系統，Tesla Model 3 以及 Tesla Model Y 將會在明日（2022 年 7 月 1 日）起生效的價目表當中，將會提供「ENHANCED AUTOPILOT」作為「可選購配件零售項目」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34-554x580.png" alt="" width="554" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34-554x580.png 554w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34-860x900.png 860w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34-768x804.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_34.png 1021w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 554px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_342.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1107865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖_2022-06-30_17_38_342.png" alt="" width="632" height="349" /></a></p><p>根據美國網頁資料，「Enhanced Autopilot」費用為 6,000 美元（約港幣 HK$47,078），包括有自動導航系統主導的自動切線功能、自動泊車功能、用家召喚汽車功能等。目前未知香港 Tesla 所提供的「Enhanced Autopilot」具備的功能是否和外國版本一樣，需要留待 Tesla 官方進一步公佈詳情。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.46.28.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1107862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.46.28.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="356" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1107860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48-1280x660.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48-768x396.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-30-17.44.48.jpg 1420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：香港海關、Tesla</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
